{"tid":1630593,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家停止裝修 全民裝飾就好了","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:37:34.000Z","uid":61690,"like":66,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"3858829e418d84a92fd9838bc5620e4474bb23da","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"都開始左裝修幾日，行動已經同對家發出清晰既訊號。毫無疑問，裝修觀感上係差。大家認真諗諗，長久裝修落去，絕對會輸輿論。<br />\n<br />\n相反，裝修完，下一步應該開始話俾街彷知點解要裝修，所以應該幫佢地裝飾，噴底點解裝修既原因上去就夠。<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n去360/麻將館度噴：福建幫斬荃灣示威者腳，以致行動不便<br />\n<br />\n唔洗粗口，唔洗屌popo，曬氣，<span style=\"color: red;\">中英文寫底原因俾街坊理解點解會俾人裝修就可以</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以智取勝，嬴輿論得天下，下一步就係解釋裝修既原因俾街坊聽</span></span>"},{"pid":"02be23a751f3da21d942c90c8a38f27d88b95ad8","tid":1630593,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"邊個大大聲話集中<br />\n<br />\n鞭屍時間<br />\n<br />\n集中撚答到我問題，先好叫人出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2d4a039c4f978afce4e7d0d8ac8a6bc72e8cbf63","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d36d25580591cee6e76e8f77dba59a993090f11c","tid":1630593,"uid":326076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"p牌 推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da4f7db72e286ffb7719f881d53ae3b7ebad7dd","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fede830385c86fc401de1dccb79327673d14741","tid":1630593,"uid":77526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:10:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e6fe549d2ce6a23c4cc385a62df01e12cfff2e1","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:11:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5a6d09eae3a5c28360db466fc84aff758d6eb35","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c53c95b0e881fbe1f65600fbfb58a220a18cb9d","tid":1630593,"uid":130400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:15:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"25c85d0e8c6019d05ecba771024e729df16f5d3c","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:15:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0655d74b0804aea288308f0a89b11f292f285cc1","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87c3209689fe24577e10dfa441c7e66dc22df71b","tid":1630593,"uid":43015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"幫吓你推"},{"pid":"44443aca842921e243d08ab56bd5c9d34fcd294b","tid":1630593,"uid":311907,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:16:31.000Z","msg":"眾所周知淋病係想將個波比番我地，再放大暴力事件。<br />\n簡單d來講，我地文宣一直講警暴，一直講五大訴求，差d乜？ 就係無將個波比番佢呀！與其成日係度話咩唔做得唔做得，不如積極 d 將所有野推番比政府？ 聽日我要見到：<br />\n<br />\n。連農牆大大隻字寫住，政府管治不力，扮對話，無真正聽市民同市威者訴求，搞到而家咁！<br />\n。等車等巴士要大大聲講，政府乜都唔做、正係識龜縮，唔肯正視問題！<br />\n。同身邊既人，無論黃藍又好，大大力屌政府無能！<br />\n<br />\n獅鳥好暴力？裝飾好暴力？咪玩啦，你唔成日提，屌番政府咪無人覺得重要囉！"},{"pid":"ea9ee8113e889e909d7545d2bf1a1c57615e12f3","tid":1630593,"uid":53610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"仲有十日就人權法，保險啲都係好事，唔好日日剩係俾人影到裝修，適宜開闢其他戰線"},{"pid":"0d88a6eb928677f6d5ae61b503fcad2a14b69f29","tid":1630593,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"畫下圖鴉都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n再貼文宣"},{"pid":"8907ab675487ac674e904319a088e1502a12881d","tid":1630593,"uid":101907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:17:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2cfbca09d72ee7089de82b27e4a68c6f89736152","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9fe7164e393f0a67486a9a8de20a96f407f202f","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5778c6534b4e199f65e5eacaaf901c58ae2ae2b8","tid":1630593,"uid":262734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:25:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"325891e97decb84e33ede65d502d8d19636a499c","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:29:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"776b56e49ba522f948da53bfc298e8aad01191e2","tid":1630593,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d337d4ac028be773c42540cd0338ba456a6441b8","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2695a12b275dab07dc3502e0c52e206b8ecb28fa","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77cd59fd043db340be5b3b57ff2fa4c77d3800ee","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a57b333c9f44b3eefcd4f3a4852583004602e2f","tid":1630593,"uid":143220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:34:24.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好屌樓主老母<br />\n顏射就好了"},{"pid":"dcda8cb05f91b611445ea31ffffd941a8d65d1dc","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74be65c93d3cd74091f27afd54e2267c04de7939","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02c39a114be4ca653cd5a1d7be49879f4f3ccc95","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:45:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c7a31f48adc05a