gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:39:31.000Z","msg":"你推唔到就岩嫁啦 左膠<br />\n中資國企都唔搞 咁你去擁抱大灣區啦！<br />\n驅除共黨 唔係淨係叫口號呀"},{"pid":"30540a7099b5f5001a2f59cf5dc4c8fa50ac0532","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:41:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82416bfaeddea721ae21214403dcedcbad77098d","tid":1630593,"uid":56425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"16e46b8fd65431f04e181bb7e93b852fc73e8c6c","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:48:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b50dda971304626f2ad374626d85b8faf8fc87c","tid":1630593,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:54:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1633005/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1633005/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">外國嘅人好幸福，一出世就生活係民主國家，有部分人根本唔會明點解我地爭取民主要用裝修、神獸（唔好高估外國人嘅智力，佢地睇野好表面）。</span><br />\n<br />\n有位巴講得好啱，我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">之所以漸漸少咗國際支持，係因為和理非戰場越來越細</span></span>。冇和理非嘅活動吸引佢地嘅眼球，餘下嘅只有神獸同裝修。<br />\n<br />\n咁所以，我地可以搞返個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">面具人鏈</span></span>，表達我地不畏反蒙面法，不畏極權嘅精神。<br />\n人鏈活動一直都比較少人被人拉，比起遊行更適合一家大細出席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且我地日日遊行，係外國人眼中好悶㗎。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">要有多啲gimmick佢地先會重新關注</span></span>。<br />\n時間、地點我唔知應該點定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但如果真係搞面具人鏈，我地可以帶上自製嘅四川面譜、facepainting、動物面膜、超人、Mario、多啦A夢、V煞⋯⋯冇嘅話純戴口罩都得，不過口罩上可以畫野。總之約精彩越好玩越好<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">依家好需要一個嘉年華式抗爭</span></span>去緩和下大家嘅情緒，同獲得國際認同。好似之前雷射革命咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果各位手足覺得呢個建議ok，就開多另一個po去講時間地點啦。<br />\n（大家都要考慮一個問題就係，面具人鏈會唔會被狗拉，如果會嘅話⋯⋯都係諗諗先。畢竟expect一家大細出席，怕會全家被告）<br />\n<br />\np牌求推"},{"pid":"9d149ab5c6f9600315a6c040d1b064002729f3d4","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:56:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2a3fffb9d05b1474afa0cc29a902697901e9a82","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:04:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b74023265e92b65459dd84ab5389ec9e86cadc68","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:11:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b1fc265c4566b139e71d8d4509c8912f3bf6c67","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:22:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"115ec285b521e712ddc3fe53e919ba46af9763ec","tid":1630593,"uid":104034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"push 支持"},{"pid":"76059f6da7de1c346a1703566c6bdfcee26fb844","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"剛柔並重 先係致勝關鍵<br />\n勇武開始要用柔啦"},{"pid":"bd21e45ca76e63422cbd6b6ab48ca195adddaab0","tid":1630593,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:16:16.000Z","msg":"達致持續進修，終身示威為目標"},{"pid":"b5d7f5c1f52073f3d5ad208059f99da9c14c1e7e","tid":1630593,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"香港人要贏就要聰明，同持久， 勇武唔可以太持久架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俾和理非玩下先"},{"pid":"7c3c3a9083407580d519c5421645973c4f8df209","tid":1630593,"uid":193253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:19:02.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"3bad0c3389c54e4bcf8595195e35b92141b4e209","tid":1630593,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:19:41.000Z","msg":"剛柔並重 先係致勝關鍵<br />\n勇武開始要用柔啦"}]}